*Treći* dan smo putovali autobusom. (We traveled by bus on the third day.)

*Treća* osoba u redu je dobila poklon. (The third person in line got a gift.)

*Trećem* mestu je pripalo prvo mesto. (Third place got the first place.)

*Trećom* smo stanju iznenada došli. (We unexpectedly arrived in the third state.)

*Trećoj* deci je najviše bilo zabavno. (The third children had the most fun.)